title: What's in it for you? Res Lease in Pflugerville. 3 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['Now, this is gorgeous!', 'Come and see this incredible 2-story, 3 bedroom, 2 and a half bathroom home in Pflugerville, TX!', "This lovely home's lower level offers carpeted and tiled flooring, an ample living and dining room that connect to an open kitchen.", 'The luminous kitchen includes wood cabinetry, plenty of counter space, a pantry, and is equipped with stainless steel appliances: refrigerator, gas stove, microwave and dishwasher.', 'The second floor features 2-bedrooms that share a full bathroom with double vanities.', "The master bedroom with its numerous windows allows sunlight to fill the room, and is equipped with a ceiling-fan, a huge full-bathroom with a double vanity, walk-in closet, walk-in shower and a bathtub, you'll never want to leave!", "Additionally, there's a laundry room inside the home with a washer and dryer unit included.", "Don't forget to check out the spacious private fenced backyard with a luscious green lawn, ideal for hosting friends and family any weekend!", 'Tour and apply today this excellent option for living today, it will lease fast!!', '**', 'In-person tours required (no exceptions)', '** all renters are enrolled in the resident benefits package.', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Cristian Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 6596598)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Benjamin Doherty, Sunroom Rentals Texas, LLC']
